<h1>Architecture</h1>
<pre class="bg-light p-3 rounded">
FilmStudio.Web (Blazor Server)
    │  REST + SignalR
    ▼
FilmStudio.Api  (:5088)
    │  JobHub  ·  FilmJobService
    ▼
FilmStudio.Engine (C#)
    · ProjectStore  (projects/, blueprint JSON)
    · GrokVideoClient (xAI videos API)
    · writes assets/video/scene_XX_clip_YY.mp4

Legacy (still useful):
  Native C# engine: Stage1/2, multi-ref video, remux/WIP, review, PDF vision
  Streamlit + Python remain as optional legacy tooling
</pre>
